                  <collation>
                    <p>The quires, signed with letters, were originally 15 in number.</p>
                  </collation>
                  <condition>
                    <list>
                      <item>
                        <p>Some of the leaves are much stained and slightly torn, especially foll. <locus from="1">1</locus>, <locus from="5">5</locus>, <locus from="7">7</locus>, <locus from="9">9</locus>, <locus from="20">20</locus>, <locus from="21">21</locus>, <locus from="27">27</locus>, <locus from="51">51</locus>, <locus from="63">63</locus>, <locus from="85">85</locus> and <locus from="90">90</locus>.</p>
                      </item>
                      <item>
                        <p><foreign xml:lang="syr">ܐ</foreign> is lost, and leaves are also wanting after foll. <locus from="4">4</locus>, <locus from="23">23</locus>, and <locus from="59">59</locus>.</p>
                      </item>
                      <item>
                        <p>The later signatures are frequently incorrect.</p>
                      </item>
